hands_on_practices.solution:
1. Relation between wavelength and healing length:
$$\lambda=2\pi\xi\;\Rightarrow\;k=\frac{2\pi}{\lambda}=\frac{2\pi}{2\pi\xi}=\frac{1}{\xi}.$$
2. Kinetic energy at this $k$:
$$\epsilon_k=\frac{\hbar^2k^2}{2m}
=\frac{\hbar^2}{2m}\frac{1}{\xi^2}
=\frac{\hbar^2}{2m}\frac{2m\mu}{\hbar^2}
=\mu.$$
3. Bogoliubov dispersion:
$$E_k=\sqrt{\epsilon_k(\epsilon_k+2\mu)}
=\sqrt{\mu(\mu+2\mu)}
=\sqrt{3\mu^2}
=\mu\sqrt{3}.$$
4. Dimensionless ratio:
$$\frac{E_k}{\mu}=\sqrt{3}.$$
